  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Histologically confirmed, CD20+ B cell diffuse large cell lymphoma, with measurable or
             evaluable disease

          -  Having no prior chemotherapy, immunotherapy or radiotherapy except for one cycle of
             CHOP or R-CHOP.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant

          -  Hepatitis B Surface Antigen positive

          -  Have known CNS disease or HIV infection

          -  Have NY Classification III or IV disease.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
